@startuml Sequence_UC04
title UC-04: Kelola Supplier

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Supplier\n(livewire/supplier)" as View
participant "Supplier\\Form\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Supplier Model" as SupplierModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /supplier
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT suppliers
DB --> Component: Collection<Supplier>
Component --> View: Render daftar supplier

== Tambah Supplier ==
User -> View: Klik Tambah Supplier\nlalu isi form lalu simpan
View -> Component: save()
Component -> Component: validate(['name'=>'required|min:3',\n'phone'=>'nullable',\n'maps_link'=>'nullable|url',\n'image'=>'nullable|image|max:2048'])
alt Validasi gagal
  Component --> View: Pesan kesalahan validasi
  View --> User: Tampilkan error
else Berhasil
  Component -> Component: Handle upload gambar jika ada
  Component -> SupplierModel: Supplier::create([...])
  SupplierModel -> DB: INSERT INTO suppliers
  DB --> SupplierModel: Supplier baru
  Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses & daftar diperbarui
end

== Ubah Supplier ==
User -> View: Klik edit, ubah data, lalu simpan
View -> Component: edit($id), save()
Component -> SupplierModel: Supplier::findOrFail($id)
SupplierModel -> DB: SELECT suppliers WHERE id = ?
DB --> SupplierModel: Supplier record
Component -> Component: validate & handle gambar baru
Component -> SupplierModel: $supplier->update([...])
SupplierModel -> DB: UPDATE suppliers SET ... WHERE id = ?
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

@enduml
